div.p:
C. Very shortly after 26 February, Asghar Moussavi-Khoeini, the link between the “students” and Khomeini, will make a public announcement that
                    all of the U.S. hostages are henceforth under the direct control of Ayatollah Khomeini. (They are, of course, now;
                    but this public statement will facilitate later negotiations.)
